I always ignore all the drama and rude comments but i feel like its time to address them. I never understood the kids who love a band and soon as the band get successful ..they automatically suck and are sell outs. I dont have time to sit home everyday and write entrys about drama, restaurants i eat at everyday and movies i sit around home watching. I apologize if thats the fun stuff you enjoy to read. If you think i was more interesting when my days consisted of being angry teenager, poor and having no career.. well im sorry that says more about your character then mine. Im 22 years old im not 18 anymore and i work alot towards something i enjoy and im happy.
There are plenty of kids who blog about doing nothing and there daily drama so do us all a favor and direct your negativity over there. Your either going to love me or hate me and im not here to try and convince you to do either. To the amazing fans who support me i appreciate every single one of you.. to the kids who spend too much time reading internet gossip and hate everything about me find something you like to focuses all your energy on, you'll be alot happier.
